hm.binkley.util.function

Interface ThrowingPredicate<T,E extends Exception>

  • Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface ThrowingPredicate<T,E extends Exception>
    ThrowingPredicate is a throwing look-a=like of Predicate. It cannot be a Predicate as it takes throwing versions of predicates. Otherwise it is a faithful reproduction.
    Author:
    B. K. Oxley (binkley)
